  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6561d84a4670ef001be42c07",
      "text": "「らむ」の使い方",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700912593
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b32",
      "text": "from [2023/11/25]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b34",
      "text": "[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911203
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d8635e90c00000f46b49",
      "text": " [はまらない形の違うひとかけら型に合わせて角を削らむ]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911203,
      "updated": 1700911204
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d85a5e90c00000f46b48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911194,
      "updated": 1700911194
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84c5e90c00000f46b47",
      "text": "「[らむ]」の使い方に自信がない[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911181,
      "updated": 1700911198
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b35",
      "text": "　2パターン考えた[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b36",
      "text": "　1. [現在推量]の[助動詞「らむ」]の場合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911234
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b37",
      "text": "　　今〇〇しているだろうなあ、という意味",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b38",
      "text": "　 活用語の[終止形]接続になるので、「削るらむ」ですね[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911214
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b39",
      "text": "　　例:[久方の 光のどけき 春の日に しづ心なく 花の散るらむ]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700925487
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3a",
      "text": "　　なるほど、身を削るらむ、角削るらむか[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3b",
      "text": "　　　[57577.icon]はまらない形の違うひとかけら型に合わせて身を削るらむ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911250
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3c",
      "text": "　　　　「ひとかけらが、身を削っているのであろう」[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3d",
      "text": "　2. 活用語の未然形+[助動詞「む」]の場合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911218
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3e",
      "text": "　　「む」は推量・意思・適当・勧誘・婉曲・仮定の意味を持つ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b3f",
      "text": "　　この歌の「削らむ」は削るの未然形「削ら」と助動詞「む」の組み合わせ[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b40",
      "text": "　　　文脈からは「よっしゃ削ろう」という意思を表すように読めた[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b41",
      "text": "　　　　勧誘的な読みもできるかも",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b42",
      "text": "　　例:[名にし負はばいざ言問はむ都鳥わが思ふ人はありやなしやと]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b43",
      "text": "　　これはこれでよいか[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b44",
      "text": "　先生ありがとう！！！[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561d84a5e90c00000f46b45",
      "text": "　　イェーイ[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1700911178,
      "updated": 1700911178
    },
    {
      "id": "6561f259be12ad00000663b0",
